snippet.title: Spirit Timer: No Escape (Teaser Trailer)
snippet.description:
If you had 30 minutes to live what would you do? Would you fight to stay alive destroying all who stood in your way. Would you make the most of what time you had left. Would you give up hope? 

SMC Games presents Spirit Timer, a new Survival Puzzler.

Credits: 
Audio: SMC Games 
Vocal Talents: Karen Dellaway
